thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc4ZoH7k.jpg&h=3d1e1fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFPeq42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFPeq42.jpg&h=a67ae412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟癲狗個煮法，不過我落咗多D冰糖，搞D少咗南乳味，屌</blockquote><br />\n好似好濃沃咁wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係唔係我想要既南乳味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，隻色都唔同<br />\n係咪因為我見佢細火炆極都唔收汁，之後落多粒冰糖再轉大多炇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf18655f4f7f7e4aed27b899903b550999f4dbeb","tid":156520,"uid":57337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:08:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>東坡肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔知點解明明煮南乳炆豬腩，最後會變左東坡肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f55fd2e4f848901e54c7e51b43dfd144c62462b","tid":156520,"uid":64259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>東坡肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔知點解明明煮南乳炆豬腩，最後會變左東坡肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n地獄廚房 食左先講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe841b0e81360148935c3594bcd538774ec3f598","tid":156520,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c4ZoH7k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc4ZoH7k.jpg&h=3d1e1fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFPeq42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFPeq42.jpg&h=a67ae412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟癲狗個煮法，不過我落咗多D冰糖，搞D少咗南乳味，屌</blockquote><br />\n好似好濃沃咁wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係唔係我想要既南乳味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，隻色都唔同<br />\n係咪因為我見佢細火炆極都唔收汁，之後落多粒冰糖再轉大多炇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用易潔獲炆係難d收汁，用中式鐵獲或不銹鋼獲炆會好炆d，我唔知你本身落左幾多糖啦，不過好有可能你糖真係落多左，其實加大個火再炆下應該ok，不過小心燶，睇個樣味道唔差呀，唔緊要啦，下次再整過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61025d1408023898cd169dc2034949f5f071fc94","tid":156520,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:17:35.000Z","msg":"好想食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4347880ab1aff09b54e152fb826c8ecc7c71fc28","tid":156520,"uid":76054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T00:42:31.000Z","msg":"D汁太稀太水色<br />\n不過應該幾好食 d肉斬得幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買左幾多肉 五花腩？"},{"pid":"02a605f22fd83e58cfce34431b508daf676919ba","tid":156520,"uid":57337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:20:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D汁太稀太水色<br />\n不過應該幾好食 d肉斬得幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買左幾多肉 五花腩？</blockquote><br />\n500g到"},{"pid":"a72bd9183e05e8c62975b2655b651964ab612f4c","tid":156520,"uid":57337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c4ZoH7k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc4ZoH7k.jpg&h=3d1e1fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFPeq42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFPeq42.jpg&h=a67ae412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟癲狗個煮法，不過我落咗多D冰糖，搞D少咗南乳味，屌</blockquote><br />\n好似好濃沃咁wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係唔係我想要既南乳味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，隻色都唔同<br />\n係咪因為我見佢細火炆極都唔收汁，之後落多粒冰糖再轉大多炇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用易潔獲炆係難d收汁，用中式鐵獲或不銹鋼獲炆會好炆d，我唔知你本身落左幾多糖啦，不過好有可能你糖真係落多左，其實加大個火再炆下應該ok，不過小心燶，睇個樣味道唔差呀，唔緊要啦，下次再整過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下次我再煮過，thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5b05f04e10986f6d54ffa3193bb4fd331e631b","tid":156520,"uid":57337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T02:22:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D汁太稀太水色<br />\n不過應該幾好食 d肉斬得幾靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買左幾多肉 五花腩？</blockquote><br />\n其實個汁個唔稀，味就唔差，有南乳味既東玻肉"},{"pid":"4f22148fbbae19e9211c7476deac9c66c46fecd2","tid":156520,"uid":74981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T03:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c4ZoH7k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc4ZoH7k.jpg&h=3d1e1fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFPeq42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFPeq42.jpg&h=a67ae412&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟癲狗個煮法，不過我落咗多D冰糖，搞D少咗南乳味，屌</blockquote><br />\n好似好濃沃咁wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係唔係我想要既南乳味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，隻色都唔同<br />\n係咪因為我見佢細火炆極都唔收汁，之後落多粒冰糖再轉大多炇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用易潔獲炆係難d收汁，用中式鐵獲或不銹鋼獲炆會好炆d，我唔知你本身落左幾多糖啦，不過好有可能你糖真係落多左，其實加大個火再炆下應該ok，不過小心燶，睇個樣味道唔差呀，唔緊要啦，下次再整過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下次我再煮過，thx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}